index.name: Open Spaces
index.description: Open Spaces is your opportunity to start or join a session on any topic under the sun. These are group discussions with no formal presentation or single presenter. Have questions about a language you don't know? Interested in sharing your experiences with others? Looking for a small conversation about who knows what? Start or join an open space!
